041500        ON    EXCEPTION
041600              DISPLAY "PC/GEV/T444/DB - ERRO OPEN TDBTAXAS"
041700              PERFORM 260-E-ERRODB   THRU    260-S-ERRODB
041800              CALL    SYSTEM         DMTERMINATE.
041900
042000
