065200*
065300*----------------------------------------------------------------*
065400*    SORTEAR VALOR
065500*----------------------------------------------------------------*
065600 120-E-SORTEAR.
065700
065800     MOVE    ZEROS               TO      AX-SORTEIO(AI1).
065900
066000***  SE NECESSARIO INICIALIZAR O SEED
066100     IF  SEED                    EQUAL   0
066200         ACCEPT  SEED            FROM    TIME
066300     ELSE
066400         NEXT SENTENCE.
066500
066600***  EFETUAR O SORTEIO
066700     CALL "RANDOM OF GENERALSUPPORT"
066800         USING   SEED
066900         GIVING  RANDOM-RESULT.
067000
067100     MOVE    RANDOM-RESULT       TO      WS-RAND.
067200
067300***  MANTER A FAIXA MINIMA JUNTO COM AS EXISTENTES
067400     IF  AI1                     =      1
067500         COMPUTE AX-SORT-SUM = AX-SORT-MIN + WS-RAND-VALUE
067600
067700         IF  AX-SORT-SUM         >       9999
067800             MOVE WS-RAND-VALUE  TO      AX-SORTEIO(AI1)
067900         ELSE
068000             MOVE AX-SORT-SUM    TO      AX-SORTEIO(AI1)
068100     ELSE
068200         MOVE WS-RAND-VALUE      TO      AX-SORTEIO(AI1).
068300
068400***  PROXIMO REGISTRO
068500     ADD     1                   TO      AI1.
068600
068700 120-S-SORTEAR.
068800     EXIT.
068900
